{"tid":1529554,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝今日一齊唱歌既手足，義載既家長，屌狗既街坊","createTime":"2019-09-01T18:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T08:40:00.000Z","uid":88169,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9210d0da879134f6874262820dde6952c17e9979","tid":1529554,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T18:20:24.000Z","msg":"好想同大家分享但ig facebook又驚有鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知而家呢個時候文宣同突發好重要，但我都想出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日段大長征真係我呢世仔行過最辛苦既最長既路，但同一班手足一路唱歌真係好開心。<br />\n<br />\n有的士狗想撞人，大家一呼百應即衝去踢車，仲有巴打屌鳩叫停既左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係好開心有你一班手足，希望我地會贏，係煲底再唱歌。<br />\n<br />\n都非常多謝一班義載家長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無你地既話我地真係大長征去比狗拉<br />\n<br />\n今日我真係好感觸，經過今日真係知道大家香港人係connect緊，我終於知我係為緊咩人去爭取。<br />\n<br />\n我愛手足，我愛香港人，我愛香港！<br />\n<br />\n光復珠海 澳門革命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">叫佔機場個手足，雖然行仆街大家都想屌，但我地都不割。 不過呢，煲底相認錫春袋就走唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"f14f85ef1dbd256d26dc74240436eb74f15016cb","tid":1529554,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T18:21:15.000Z","msg":"推到兄弟見到"},{"pid":"474a4058953f4990e66780793b9947fe797487b0","tid":1529554,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T18:21:52.000Z","msg":"推到姊妹見到"},{"pid":"1ddc16a4670926b678eb4c9b1c6d0948393598c4","tid":1529554,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T18:22:02.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"7b81244f68999f30ca18eea1d4073be904eb17ec","tid":1529554,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T18:22:12.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"4338f83540afea6a6a379531dd0cdbaecf8cdb12